<div class='card--resource__body'>
<h2 class="card--resource__title">How Do I Escape Regret over Hurt I’ve Caused?</h2>
<div class='card--resource__date'>Jun 5, 2017</div>
<div class="card--resource__text">Don’t be paralyzed by feelings of regret. Rather let those very feelings empower you with a sense of greater grace, gratitude, and joy in God’s grace.


</div></div>
