<h2 class="card--resource__title">Do You Know Your Greatest Problem?</h2>
<h3 class='card--resource__subtitle'>The Good News of Christianity</h3>
<div class='card--resource__date'>Jun 6, 2017</div>
<div class="card--resource__text">Your biggest problem is not your old car, your mundane job, or your broken family. Your biggest problem is your sin.


