<h2 class="card--resource__title">Are You Too Christian for Non-Christians?</h2>
<div class='card--resource__date'>Jun 21, 2014</div>
<div class="card--resource__text">Many Christians find over time that they have fewer non-Christian friends and acquaintances. Here are seven simple steps to boost your personal evangelism.


</div></div>
